headline: How Should Investors Value CME Group After a 32% Rally in 2025?
summary: If you find yourself pondering whether CME Group is still a smart buy, you are not alone. This is especially true after its impressive run in recent months. The stock has seen notable gains, up 3.1% over the past week and 6.4% in the last month. This builds on a strong year-to-date return of 22.5% and an impressive 32.2% gain over the past year.
